{
  "stem": "13258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said he was the son of one of my grandfather's-- my father's former partners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a reserve officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Guttmann, the Russians are coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father said, are they going with us or against us?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, that, we don't know yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to sleep, and in the morning, we heard that the Russians had come, but we didn't see any.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, that was at that place, and that lieutenant had told us, get out from here, and see that you get into a big town, because in the small places, it's going to be terrible.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we first went back to Zbarazh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We hired another farmer, this time only one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all squeezed into one wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Money was running short.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went back to Zbar-- to [INAUDIBLE] on the border-- not Zbarazh, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went back to [INAUDIBLE], stayed in [INAUDIBLE] eight days, until the first train wasn't--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, one day, a troop, a group of Russians came on a truck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the first Russians we saw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It turned out, they were from the fire department, the reason being that the fire department in Russia is part of the Ministry of the Interior.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the Ministry of the Interior doesn't take care of forests, but this is the Ministry of the Police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the fire department was subordinated to the police, because when there is a fire, there is suspicions that it is sabotage.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that were the first Russians we saw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When a train came, finally, it consisted of one freight car, a wood-fired locomotive, a-- two people, two engineers on the locomotive, and an officer from the tank trucks, tank-- our tank, some tank groups-- you could see by his insignia-- as the escort.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
